                  "revisionId": 2768443,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "At max rank, the listed 270% success chance means that the Kubrow will always dig up two items, with a 70% chance of a third item."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Dig",
                  "pageId": 510260,
                  "revisionId": 2768443,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "When in use, the Kubrow will bark twice to notify the player, stop at a location and paw along the ground for 5 seconds, before barking twice to alert players of its find."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Dig",
                  "pageId": 510260,
                  "revisionId": 2768443,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The mods that may occasionally be dug up are taken from the same mod list used by Void containers."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Dig",
                  "pageId": 510260,
                  "revisionId": 2768443,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Kubrow prioritize items depending on its master's needs: if their master needs energy, Energy Orbs are retrieved, if they need ammunition, the relevant ammo type is retrieved, etc."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Dig",
                  "pageId": 510260,
                  "revisionId": 2768443,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The threshold values for energy and health orb prioritization seem to be 80% (or lower) of total energy/health capacity."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Dig",
                  "pageId": 510260,
                  "revisionId": 2768443,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Ammo is retrieved upon not having full reserves."
                }
              },
